                                                                                                        <a href="https://en.annahar.com/author/7565-georgi-azar">Georgi Azar</a> </span> <h4>27 May 2019 | 18:42</h4> <h4>Source: by Annahar</h4> </div> </div> <ul class="author desktop"> <li>by
                                                                                                        <a href="https://en.annahar.com/author/7565-georgi-azar">Georgi Azar</a> </li> <li>Source: Annahar</li> <li itemprop="datePublished" content="2019-05-27T13:42">Date added: 27 May 2019</li> <li>Last update: 27 May 2019 | 18:42</li> </ul> <ul class="social_share top"> <li><a class="facebook_icon" target="_blank" data-shorturl="https%3A%2F%2Fen.annahar.com%2Farticle%2F977165-lebanons-cabinet-set-to-endorse-austerity-budget" onclick="var sTop = window.screen.height/2-(218); var sLeft = window.screen.width/2-(313);window.open(this.href,'sharer','toolbar=0,status=0,width=626,height=256,top='+sTop+',left='+sLeft);return false;" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.annahar.com%2Farticle%2F977165&utm_campaign=sharebar&utm_medium=facebook"><span class="fbShares desktop" data-articleid="977165">-</span><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li> <li><a class="twitter_icon" href="https://www.twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.annahar.com%2Farticle%2F977165&via=AnnaharEn&text=Lebanon's Cabinet endorses austerity budget&utm_campaign=sharebar&utm_medium=twitter" data-count="none" data-size="large" data-url="https://en.annahar.com/article/977165" data-via="AnnaharEn" data-lang="en" onclick="var sTop = window.screen.height/2-(218); var sLeft = window.screen.width/2-(313);window.open(this.href,'sharer','toolbar=0,status=0,width=626,height=256,top='+sTop+',left='+sLeft);return false;"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a></li> <li><a class="linkedin_icon" href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.annahar.com%2Farticle%2F977165&utm_campaign=sharebar&utm_medium=linkedin" target="_blank" data-count="none" data-size="large" data-url="https://en.annahar.com/article/977165" data-via="annahar" data-lang="en" onclick="var sTop = window.screen.height/2-(218); var sLeft = window.screen.width/2-(313);window.open(this.href,'sharer','toolbar=0,status